# Organize Frontend Project Files Walkthrough

## Summary of Changes
1. **Created New Directory**: We successfully created the `GPSDeniedDroneInteractiveDocumentation` directory at the root of your repository to house all your frontend projects.
2. **Moved Directories**: The `Frontend`, `Frontend3D`, and `aero-controllers-3d` folders were moved inside `GPSDeniedDroneInteractiveDocumentation`.
3. **Updated GitHub Actions Workflow**: Modified [.github/workflows/nextjs.yml](file:///s:/GPSDeniedDroneDocumentation/.github/workflows/nextjs.yml) so the GitHub Pages deployment process correctly paths into `GPSDeniedDroneInteractiveDocumentation/aero-controllers-3d/` for its cache and correct working directory.

